@startuml 图4-2 成果提交审核时序图
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000

actor "教师" as Teacher
participant "EduAchievement\nController" as Ctrl
participant "IEduAchievement\nService" as Service
participant "EduAchievement\nMapper" as Mapper
participant "MySQL\nedu_achievement" as DB

Teacher -> Ctrl : POST /achievement/teacherAddAchievement\n{title, content, category, ...}

Ctrl -> Ctrl : SecurityUtils.getUserId()\n强制绑定当前教师ID
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 校验状态合法性\n(0或2)

Ctrl -> Service : insertEduAchievement(achievement)
Service -> Service : if status not in [0,2]\n    setStatus("0")
Service -> Service : setCreateTime(now)
Service -> Mapper : insertEduAchievement(achievement)
Mapper -> DB : INSERT INTO edu_achievement\n(title, content, teacher_id, status, ...)
DB --> Mapper : 1 row

Mapper --> Service : success
Service --> Ctrl : 1
Ctrl --> Teacher : AjaxResult.success

note over Teacher, DB
  成果状态为草稿(0)或审核中(2)
  教师可后续通过teacherUpdate修改
  通过teacherResubmit重新提交
  通过teacherWithdraw撤回审核
end note

@enduml
